==English==

===Etymology===
From a [[portmanteau]] of [[lava]] and [[icicle]].

===Noun===
'''lavacicle'''
#A [[geological]] [[formation]] consisting of a quantity of lava that [[dripped]] from the roof of a [[cave]] as it cooled and hardened, leaving a rounded protrusion.

